description:
The Butcher came to US as a skilled wrestler. In her first match up she upset Devi Lynn to the shock of all US Fans. She then went on to destroy The Terminator who had 5 inches and almost 40lbs on her. The Butcher feels no pain, and never lets up even for a second on the mat.
Vendetta is the Champion. This will be a good test to see where Madison fits into the scheme of things.
title: Vendetta (11-3)
